***Oppo Band smart bracelet - Impressive design
--Oppo Band smart bracelet launched in mid-June with a youthful and dynamic appearance, sharp 1.1-inch Amoled screen and huge battery capacity. This will certainly be a formidable smartwatch competitor that competes directly with the Xiaomi Mi Band 5.

